https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null This video gives audience members a first-class ticket on cruises to six islands in Hawaii and French Polynesia. The ravishing scenery -- pristine beaches, lush forests, dormant volcanoes -- dominates the itinerary. Stops include Hawaii, Huahine, Kauai, Lanai, Maui, Molokai, Oahu, Bora Bora, Moorea, Raiatea, Rangiroa and Tahiti. A "Top 10 Attractions" special feature spotlights surfing at Waikiki Beach and swimming with sharks in Bora Bora. Cruise Hawaii & Tahiti
